Problabs, the company behind AgentsBids was founded in early 2012, We work out of a sweet li’l office in Chandigarh, India.

we came together as a team of passionate people who wanted to build something amazing. We are committed to building great services products that work for you: simplifying your life and saving you money. These products will listen to your preferences and take action for you and with your permission.

We love saving people money! Here at AgentsBids.com our team is dedicated to one single goal and that is helping people like you save a fortune by comparison shopping. We shop all the major products carriers to help you find the lowest possible rate.

We believe in 4 key tenets at AgentsBids:

QUALITY IN EVERYTHING WE DO

BE ENTREPRENEURIAL HAVE FUN,

STAY SANE,

TAKE CARE BE TRANSPARENT
